<br>
How is this balanced. Their spells outdamage us and they get a pet. I LOVE my wizard and there are MANY wizards on my server (easier to tell nowadays with familiars). This really disheartens me as I'm more or less useless if there is a mage nearby. Can someone console me please? Tell me we're good! Please!<br>
<br>
What advantages do we have (aside from the obvious: We're smarter, better looking, and we have ports)<br>
<br>
Thanks!<br>
